An '''audio telescope''' was a form of technology that recorded conversations. It was small enough to hide in plain sight and could be attached to walls or ceilings.

One was used by [[Hiram Drayson/Legends|Hiram Drayson]] to eavesdrop on [[Nil Spaar]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]].

